@model VMbestellingen;

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>BestelBevestiging</title>
</head>
<body class="m-3">
    <h2 class="text-center"><img class="artikelKlein" src="~/images/HighSpiritsLogo.png" /> - Bestellingsbevestiging </h2>
    <div class="position-relative m-4">
        <div class="progress" style="height: 1px;">
            <div class="progress-bar bg-dark" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%;" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
        </div>
        <button type="button" class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 translate-middle btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded-pill" style="width: 2rem; height:2rem;">1</button>
        <button type="button" class="position-absolute top-0 start-50 translate-middle btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded-pill" style="width: 2rem; height:2rem;">2</button>
        <button type="button" class="position-absolute top-0 start-100 translate-middle btn btn-sm btn-dark rounded-pill" style="width: 2rem; height:2rem;">3</button>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
        <p>We hebben u bestelling met bestelnummer <span class="fw-bold"> @Model.bestelling.BestellingId </span> goed ontvangen.</p>
        <p>Na overschrijving van <span class="fw-bold">€ @Model.totalen.PrijsInclusief </span> op rekeningnummer <span class="fw-bold">BE41 0019 4020 4710</span> worden de goederen verpakt en verstuurd.</p>
        <p>U ontving deze bevestiging ook via e-mail.</p>
        <p>Bedankt voor u vertrouwen.</p>
        <p class="text-center"><a asp-action="Index" class="geenLijn">Ga terug naar catalogus...</a></p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
